---
title: American-Style Black Bean Chilli with Radish Salsa, Corn Chips & Sour Cream
description: Spice up dinner time with a black bean chilli, all the punchy flavours without the heat. We suggest grabbing a corn
chip and piling up a helping of saucy beans and sour cream. Chase it down with a cucumber salsa, for that fresh kick
every chilli bowl needs.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6481673838f49a2a03a2f037-7c03113c.jpeg
